metadata.name: PEPE The Mad Frog
metadata.description:
In a galaxy far far away, six elemental crystals are huddling across the universe. These Ethereum stones each control an essential aspect of existence. PEPE, the mad frog plans to harness their power to summon more various versions of himself!!

---
Size: 2160x2700px
Duration: 15 seconds
Format: MP4 with audio
